"48DNXA07.0GB", "(XB114_030)", and "2011/04/13" is silkscreened :on the wireless modules in the FCC photos. This device is the dual channel, dual band version of the [[Netgear WNDAP620|WNDAP620]]. :Two (dual-band) DNXA-G1's would appear to be used. Per '''/proc/pci/devices''' output from a device, each uses :a 168c:0030 PCI ID (default for [[Atheros]] AR938x).
